snippet.textDisplay:
You simply murdered the song! OMG! Jara original ei gaan shunechen, tara janen, Shahnaz Rahmatullah r level kothay! Ota chowa jaay na, onubhob kora jaay maatro. Blues kivabe banglay gawa jaay Shahnaz holen best example. 
Ei meyeta janei na blues and jazz er difference ki! Ki darun ekta rhythm and blues gaan peculiar husky korar bertho cheshta korlo. Kalwati korlei ki ucchango shangeet hoy? kintu ganer aabohe dress up aar shaaj deya holo. Shudhu gaan ta e holo na. Ki voyongkor! Music sonded so blunt! Horrendous! 
This total thing made me depressed and angry. Extremely disappointed. Please do not even try to touch Shahnaz's songs. This is not for everyone!
Arnob, you can do better than this. Come on!
